        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Commission on United States Occupations Act or the La Comisi&oacute;n de las ocupaciones norteamericanas Act</b></p> <p>This bill establishes the Commission to Study and Develop Reconciliation Proposals for Dominican Republic.</p> <p>The commission must address specified U.S. actions related to the Dominican Republic (e.g., military occupations and efforts to annex the Dominican Republic) and make recommendations for appropriate remedies, including a formal apology and repair and reconciliation efforts. </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
